mod_spox
    http://modspox.rubyforge.org
    Author: spox
    
== Description

A Ruby IRC bot

== Usage

Configuration:

mod_spox --config

Running:

mod_spox

== Requirements

 * sequel
  * database driver
 
== Optional

 * fastthread
 
== Install

sudo gem install --include-dependencies mod_spox

